    </div>
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A comprehensive briefing on the new Cuba sanctions authority, GAESA designation, MOA Nickel, and the June 5 wind-down deadline for foreign persons.</p>
    <div class="meta">
      <span><strong>Published</strong> May 13, 2026</span>
      <span><strong>Last updated</strong> May 13, 2026</span>
      <span><strong>Read</strong> 18 min</span>
